{"tid":624352,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"求指數期權高手教路","createTime":"2018-04-10T18:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T10:46:51.000Z","uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b15f69336a57bd13636ce823d1fc04fd1c40968c","tid":624352,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T18:42:23.000Z","msg":"我係期權新手，<br />\n想知如果我買小恒指4月期權 32000 LC<br />\n，當依家細期係報30000點，<br />\n而期權金要比300點x每點$10=$3,000<br />\n<br />\n一星期後細期升1000點，作31000，<br />\n32000 LC 期權金升到 500點&times;每點$10=$5,000<br />\n<br />\n我想平倉咁應該點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就我所知係應該買入同數量既 32000 SC，收期權金。但如果係咁我個倉唔係會變左做同時持有32000 LC同SC？定係佢會識得自動扺消？咁我Totally一共賺幾多期權金？同交易費又會點計？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我上網搵左一斷時間都唔太清楚，唔該哂咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56b89ae7cf91c5394f678910ef92e7e9c8f428b","tid":624352,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"lc 完再sc 同日子同價位等於平左倉<br />\n一通都會show 做持有0<br />\n<br />\n如果lc 同sc 唔同價位，就係做spread"},{"pid":"b5575e9df827c16b7c506b5f93156090fe4e8a89","tid":624352,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T18:47:13.000Z","msg":"你個case 賺$2000,<br />\n手續費睇你間行"},{"pid":"1507e395359efe8992bf9c5cb0cce8a8d088e38d","tid":624352,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c56b89ae7cf91c5394f678910ef92e7e9c8f428b","tid":624352,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"lc 完再sc 同日子同價位等於平左倉<br />\n一通都會show 做持有0<br />\n<br />\n如果lc 同sc 唔同價位，就係做spread"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T18:53:42.000Z","msg":"唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但如果係同價位(32000)但唔同日子做LC SC(4月2號32000 LC，4月21號32000 SC)，咁依個又係咪平左倉？有冇咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb8776a04dcc0633e21c6f8da45f7300be37c87","tid":624352,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T19:04:51.000Z","msg":"另外，<br />\n我睇既書就話 期權金=價內值+時間值<br />\n但我留意到，<br />\n當4月1號 細期：30000<br />\n32000LC 期權金= 500&times;$10=$5,000<br />\n4月3號 細期：31000<br />\n32000LC 期權金= 700$10=$7,000<br />\n<br />\n其實點解會有依個情況出現？因為理論上32000係價外期權，佢未有內在價值，只有時間值。咁理論上32000 LC 既期權金唔係會因為除住時間流失而減價？點解個期權金仲會升？(而我發覺價外期權升既幅度甚至比價內期權總要高，會唔會係關delta事？)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11da156ad404fde390617b1d0f1fa8c6515342df","tid":624352,"uid":72734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T21:03:42.000Z","msg":"你好多嘢都未識<br />\n建議你唔好入場住"},{"pid":"500870bb1689e3b8cc68959cb3cfbb7dccc4d826","tid":624352,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T21:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，<br />\n我睇既書就話 期權金=價內值+時間值<br />\n但我留意到，<br />\n當4月1號 細期：30000<br />\n32000LC 期權金= 500&times;$10=$5,000<br />\n4月3號 細期：31000<br />\n32000LC 期權金= 700$10=$7,000<br />\n<br />\n其實點解會有依個情況出現？因為理論上32000係價外期權，佢未有內在價值，只有時間值。咁理論上32000 LC 既期權金唔係會因為除住時間流失而減價？點解個期權金仲會升？(而我發覺價外期權升既幅度甚至比價內期權總要高，會唔會係關delta事？)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恒指月頭2日升1000點 你點解覺得張LC 係會跌？？"},{"pid":"c7c6965be4d33250a8d763a31685e145bdba2168","tid":624352,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500870bb1689e3b8cc68959cb3cfbb7dccc4d826","tid":624352,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T21:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，<br />\n我睇既書就話 期權金=價內值+時間值<br />\n但我留意到，<br />\n當4月1號 細期：30000<br />\n32000LC 期權金= 500&times;$10=$5,000<br />\n4月3號 細期：31000<br />\n32000LC 期權金= 700$10=$7,000<br />\n<br />\n其實點解會有依個情況出現？因為理論上32000係價外期權，佢未有內在價值，只有時間值。咁理論上32000 LC 既期權金唔係會因為除住時間流失而減價？點解個期權金仲會升？(而我發覺價外期權升既幅度甚至比價內期權總要高，會唔會係關delta事？)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恒指月頭2日升1000點 你點解覺得張LC 係會跌？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T21:34:35.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n<br />\n期權個價就係有幾多機會到價<br />\n你1個月內入價張野先價錢 你要2000點<br />\n依加當20個交易日 1日搞掂一半<br />\n到價既機會大增 我肯定張野升唔少<br />\n<br />\n當然實際要計埋其他野"},{"pid":"7eb3e88ea48bb354cf85874393288fae140c8bc2","tid":624352,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1507e395359efe8992bf9c5cb0cce8a8d088e38d","tid":624352,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c56b89ae7cf91c5394f678910ef92e7e9c8f428b","tid":624352,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"lc 完再sc 同日子同價位等於平左倉<br />\n一通都會show 做持有0<br />\n<br />\n如果lc 同sc 唔同價位，就係做spread"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T18:53:42.000Z","msg":"唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但如果係同價位(32000)但唔同日子做LC SC(4月2號32000 LC，4月21號32000 SC)，咁依個又係咪平左倉？有冇咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:52:23.000Z","msg":"係。同日子講緊結算日：即月、下月、後月"},{"pid":"7d49dbecb10ca0c8c75637ac152b79ecebc80c45","tid":624352,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:57:15.000Z","msg":"總之樓主做返同一個號碼嘅Short call就得啦"},{"pid":"9a6959801873bdf662e726dab0ba78979c9ff369","tid":624352,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d49dbecb10ca0c8c75637ac152b79ecebc80c45","tid":624352,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:57:15.000Z","msg":"總之樓主做返同一個號碼嘅Short call就得啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"等陣short 錯唔同月份就痾不甩"},{"pid":"cc883f3ddca4265392dd2a5ac16c4ecdae2eb34d","tid":624352,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T00:19:00.000Z","msg":"LC SC 同一樣野同一數量就會自動offs